headline: Government votes against delaying pullout
description: Government ministers voted to reject a proposal by Yisrael Katz to delay the disengagement plan by 3 months.    18 ministers voted against the bill, while 3 voted in favor: Katz, Health Minister Danny Naveh, and Finance Minister Benjamin Netanyahu. (Diana Bahur-Nir)
